data.description: PRICE REDUCED BELOW RECENT APPRAISED VALUE!! One or more photo(s) have been Virtually Staged.     BUY-DOWN YOUR INTEREST RATE!! Seller is offering to Buy-Down the Interest Rate or Pay Closing Costs up to a maximum of $10,000 with an Acceptable Offer. Beautifully remodelled, GREAT FOR ENTERTAINING OR MULTI-GENERATIONAL FAMILY. MASSIVE home with over 3500 sq. ft in the heart of the South Tampa area! Bring your BOAT. Home is located within 5 minutes of several MARINAS!! Features include 5 bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, Family Room, DEN/OFFICE, Living Room, BONUS/GAMEROOM, and GUEST QUARTERS/ In-Law (with its own kitchen). This spacious, light and airy, open floor plan offers Freshly painted interior and exterior, RECESSED LIGHTING, custom trim work, CROWN MOLDING, a large open kitchen with wood cabinets, GRANITE countertops, STAINLESS-STEEL appliances, SMART THERMOSTAT, TILE flooring throughout, and BEAMED ceil-ing in the Dining Room. Large GUEST QUARTERS offers a Living/Dining area with a bonus kitchen, GRAN-ITE countertop, a deep double Stainless Steel sink, wood cabinetry, a SPACIOUS bedroom with its own FULL BATHROOM, recently upgraded tile shower and loads of closet space. New CEILING FANS IN 2022/2023, LARGE laundry room with washer & dryer, SLIDING DOORS to backyard and patio, more than enough storage with a 14 x 30 shed, newly landscaped grounds and Newer Fully VINYL fenced backyard in 2020/2021. CENTRALLY-LOCATED! Very close to Tampa International Airport, MacDill AFB, Amalie Arena and the beautiful Sparkman Wharf. Less than 30 minutes to RENOWNED BEACHES and minutes from great RESTAURANTS, live MUSIC, THEATERS, MUSEUMS, BIKING TRAILS, LAKES, DOG PARKS, PLAYGROUNDS, and so much more! N.B.: *Buy-Down or Closing Costs limits will be subject to the Buyers' loan program/lender guidelines*
